Building for the agent economyAgents represent an entirely new category of users to build for—and increasingly, sell to. Stripe is building a broad set of agentic financial infrastructure to enable these important new patterns, via our Agentic Commerce Suite, Agentic Commerce Protocol (ACP), MCP integrations, and payment support for both MPP and x402. To get started with MPP using Stripe, read our docs and sign up for early access.
